### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888
@clientId = {{$dotenv GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID}}
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Test Auth Function
GET {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/auth
Accept: application/json

### Test Debug Function
GET {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/debug
Accept: application/json

### Test Token Validation
GET {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/validate-token
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test OAuth URL (Manual)
GET https://accounts.google.com/o/oauth2/v2/auth?client_id={{clientId}}&redirect_uri={{baseUrl}}/auth/callback&response_type=code&scope=email%20profile%20openid

### Test Callback (with mock code)
GET {{baseUrl}}/.netlify/functions/auth-callback?code=mock-auth-code&state=random-state

### Test Protected Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}